Two maps from 1.6 ported to CS:S.
They include:
ivns_lazybl0ck
notkz_earlyspring

An earlier version of notkz_earlyspring is included with all skips left unpatched.

As per usual, if any of the original authors has an issue with any of their work being recreated, please contact me ASAP and I will remove the map(s) at once, no questions asked.
